{
  "id": "69cdd9396ddf6d12bdf751a1",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:なろう系イントロテンプレ",
  "created": 1775098193,
  "updated": 1775098232,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69cdd9396ddf6d12bdf751a1",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:なろう系イントロテンプレ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098193,
      "updated": 1775098193
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95100000000000f8874",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098193,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8875",
      "text": "「はいどーも！本日のゆるトーク会は〜『[なろう系イントロテンプレ]』についてでーす！いぇい！転生！無双！チート！テンプレ三銃士きたこれ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098206
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8876",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8877",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8878",
      "text": "「分類すると、その三要素は“導入フックの高速化”と“読者期待の即時満足”に寄与する設計だね。合理的。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8879",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f887a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f887b",
      "text": "「“導入フック”というのは、物語の最初で読者の心を惹きつける工夫、という意味でよろしいかしら」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f887c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f887d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f887e",
      "text": "「そう。冒頭数ページで“続きを読む理由”を提示する。いわばプロダクトのオンボーディング。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f887f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8880",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8881",
      "text": "「出た、急にIT用語w つまり“最初でハマらせるやつ”ってことね！OK理解！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8882",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8883",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8884",
      "text": "「（微笑）たしかに、物語のはじまりで世界が開ける瞬間は、とても大切ですものね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8885",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8886",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8887",
      "text": "「でさ、その“なろう系イントロテンプレ”って、だいたいこうじゃん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8888",
      "text": " 1. 現実でちょい不遇な主人公",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8889",
      "text": " 2. なんかのきっかけで異世界へGO",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f888a",
      "text": " 3. 気づいたら最強スキル持ち",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f888b",
      "text": " 4. 周り『え、なにそれすご…』ってなる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f888c",
      "text": "はい優勝」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f888d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f888e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f888f",
      "text": "「要点整理するね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8890",
      "text": " 初期状態：共感しやすい課題設定",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8891",
      "text": " イベント：転移・転生という非日常トリガー",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8892",
      "text": " 能力付与：チートスキルで優位性確保",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8893",
      "text": " 反応：周囲の評価でカタルシス生成",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8894",
      "text": "構造としてはかなり完成度が高い。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8895",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8896",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8897",
      "text": "「うわ、急に論文っぽくなったw でもわかる〜。気持ちいいんよね、あの“俺つえー”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8898",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f8899",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f889a",
      "text": "「その“気持ちよさ”は、読者が主人公に心を重ねることで生まれるのですね。現実で抱える思いが、物語の中でやさしくほどけるような…（遠くを見る）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f889b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f889c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f889d",
      "text": "「おお、急に文学の風が吹いた」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f889e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f889f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a0",
      "text": "「心理的には“自己効力感の補完”とも言える。自分にもできるかもしれない、という感覚の代理体験。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a3",
      "text": "「つまり、ゲームでレベル1からいきなり最強装備もらう感じ？神ゲーやん」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a5",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a6",
      "text": "「そういう比喩は的確。初期ストレスを排除して、コア体験に直行する設計。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a8",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88a9",
      "text": "「ただ、その分、ゆっくりと積み重ねる成長の物語とは、また違った味わいになりますね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ab",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ac",
      "text": "「たしかに！“コツコツ型主人公”も好きだけど、なろう系は“ショートカット最強ルート”って感じ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ae",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88af",
      "text": "「どちらもユーザー体験として成立している。ターゲットと目的が違うだけ。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b2",
      "text": "「ユーザーって言うなw 夢見させてw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b4",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b5",
      "text": "「（笑う）でも、読者を大切に思う気持ちは、きっと同じですわね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b8",
      "text": "「でさでさ、テンプレって言われがちだけど、それって悪いことなの？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ba",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88bb",
      "text": "「一概にはそうとも限らない。テンプレは“再利用可能な成功パターン”。効率よく満足度を提供できる。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88bc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88bd",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88be",
      "text": "「お、ポジティブ解釈きた！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c0",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c1",
      "text": "「安心して物語に入れる、という良さもありますね。“こういうお話かもしれない”と想像できるのは、読書の助けになりますもの」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c4",
      "text": "「たしかに、“はいはいこの流れね”って思いながらも読むの、なんか楽しいんよねw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c6",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c7",
      "text": "「ただし、差別化も重要。テンプレ＋独自要素で“記憶に残る作品”になる。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88c9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ca",
      "text": "「出た、“＋αが大事”ってやつ！例えば？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88cc",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88cd",
      "text": "「例えば、スキルの制約条件をユニークにする、世界観に明確なルールを設ける、あるいはキャラクターの動機を深掘りするなど。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88cf",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d0",
      "text": "「小さな違いが、やがて大きな個性となるのですね。まるで同じ旋律でも、奏でる人によって響きが変わるように」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d3",
      "text": "「詩人きたこれ。じゃあ私も言うわ、“テンプレは土台、クセはスパイス！”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d5",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d6",
      "text": "「悪くない表現。簡潔で伝わる。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d8",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88d9",
      "text": "「（微笑）とても愛らしい言い回しです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88db",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88dc",
      "text": "「よっしゃ褒められた！で、まとめると〜？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88de",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88df",
      "text": "「要点：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e0",
      "text": " なろう系イントロは“即フック＋即カタルシス”の設計",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e1",
      "text": " テンプレは効率的な成功パターン",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e2",
      "text": " 独自要素で作品の価値が上がる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e3",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e6",
      "text": "「完璧すぎて教科書かよw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e8",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88e9",
      "text": "「けれど、その中にも書き手の想いが宿るのが、物語の魅力ですわね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88eb",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ec",
      "text": "「いいこと言う〜。じゃあ今日はこのへんで！みんなも異世界転生するときはテンプレ忘れずに！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ee",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88ef",
      "text": "「現実世界での実装は未確認だけどね。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f2",
      "text": "「いやそれはそうwww」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f4",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f5",
      "text": "「（笑う）どうか安全第一で」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd95200000000000f88f8",
      "text": "「オチが現実的すぎる！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098194,
      "updated": 1775098194
    },
    {
      "id": "69cdd96c00000000000f88f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775098220,
      "updated": 1775098220
    },
